headline: Unpacking Q4 Earnings: Xylem (NYSE:XYL) In The Context Of Other Water Infrastructure Stocks
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how water infrastructure stocks fared in Q4, starting with Xylem (NYSE:XYL).
